comments: Robinson-Earl (OKC) trips Young (SAS) and affects his SQBR during the driving shot attempt.
Muscala (OKC) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Dort (OKC) legally contests Murray's (SAS) jump shot attempt.
Muscala (OKC) makes contact to Vassell's (SAS) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Johnson (SAS) makes marginal contact with Dort (OKC) that does not affect his shot attempt at the basket.
Bazley (OKC) makes contact with Walker IV's (SAS) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Dort (OKC) makes marginal contact with his off-arm to Young (SAS) during the drive to the basket.
Young (SAS) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Dort (OKC) and marginal contact occurs as the two players meet.
Dort (OKC) jumps into Johnson (SAS) and makes contact that affects his shot attempt.
Murray (SAS) makes contact with Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) that affects his ability to make the pass.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) legally contests Walker IV's (SAS) jump shot attempt.
Vassell (SAS) commits a take foul on Muscala (OKC).
